《'''1世代：我們的世代'''》（{{lang-en|''One Direction: This Is Us''}}）是2013年由英国-爱尔兰男子团体[[1世代|1世代]]出演的一部[[3D電影|3D]]纪录式电影。电影主要讲述了1世代全球巡演的點滴，穿插了团体在倫敦[[O2體育館|O<sub>2</sub>體育館]]演唱會演出的镜头。<ref>{{cite web|title=One Direction: ''This Is Us'' in 3D|url=http://www.fandango.com/onedirection:thisisus_v566167/plotsummary|publisher=Fandango|accessdate=2017-02-27|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214063837/http://www.fandango.com/onedirection:thisisus_v566167/plotsummary|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=One Direction:This is Us|url=http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/onedirection/|publisher=Sony Pictures|accessdate=2013-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925193737/http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/onedirection/|archive-date=2013-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Harp|first=Justin|title=Simon Cowell: Morgan Spurlock will make One Direction 3D film interesting|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a439273/simon-cowell-morgan-spurlock-will-make-one-direction-3d-film-interesting.html|publisher=Digital Spy|accessdate=2017-02-27|archive-date=2013-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925045632/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a439273/simon-cowell-morgan-spurlock-will-make-one-direction-3d-film-interesting.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>电影于2013年8月20日在英国[[萊斯特廣場|萊斯特廣場]][[首演|首演]]，并于29日在英国正式上映。《我們的世代》 在北美取得了$28,873,376票房收入，在其它国家则取得了$38,455,345票房收入，全球票房收入总共为$67,328,742<ref name="mojo"/>，成为史上票房收入第4高的音乐会电影。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=musicconcert.htm|title=Box Office Mojo highest grossing concert films|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2013-09-01|archive-date=2012-09-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AlKyBXFi?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=musicconcert.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>电影上映后获得了褒贬不一的影评，影片在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据85份影片获得64新鲜度。<ref name="tomatoes">{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/this_is_us/ | title = One Direction: This Is Us (2013) | publisher =  | work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate = 2013-08-30 | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111213015/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/this_is_us | dead-url = no }}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，影片则获得49分综评。<ref>{{metacritic film|one-direction-this-is-us|One Direction: This Is Us}} Retrieved 29 August 2013</ref>

